Invoicing templates
This invoice template can be used to bill your clients in order to collect payments. This template
contains the basic information typically contained in an invoice such as the invoice amount, the
services/products provided and the payment due date. Follow the instructions contained in the
template and review the second page for a filled out example. This document is ideal for small
businesses that want to invoice clients and receive timely payments.
